{"tid":1776404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇黎完左區選又到樽頸位 身邊人都諗聖誕去邊去","createTime":"2019-12-09T13:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T13:57:26.000Z","uid":68943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"387944f62d4a6c9b0c8f8c5f4123f250aca10bc7","tid":1776404,"uid":68943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:42:26.000Z","msg":"真開心 最憎人ig扮到有幾黃咪又係吃喝玩樂"},{"pid":"02f429012f4de87e9daae2f851fb36bd5811612e","tid":1776404,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n昨日遊行最深刻的一句「初夏&mdash;&mdash;寒冬」<br />\n我們不經不覺由初夏走到冬天<br />\n由撐黃色食店走到黃色經濟圈<br />\n香港人就是有心有力也有財力<br />\n<br />\n講返正題，以往每年聖誕聯歡/Re-U都總係會叫啲最方便快捷嘅KFC、PizzaHut聖誕套餐，今年相信大家都不了不了，所以我地整合左所有會做到會服務嘅黃店，大家識Do啦！<br />\n*（亦建議學生會將圖印出派比同學宣傳📃）<br />\n<br />\n最後，教育同行全體祝大家有個Yellow Christmas 🎄💛<br />\n<br />\n*我地已盡量向店方直接確認到會服務，但始終人手有限，資料未必齊全，歡迎各位Comment報料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTg: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkteacher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkteacher&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2FwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=8fd53609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkteacher</a><br />\nFb: shorturl.at/kqtJM<br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstandbyeducatorshk%3Figshid%3Djuzv8s7rtxb5&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2FwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=742eebd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5</a>"},{"pid":"86e3481e003a3dddfb6d72035b3cf48e4d2411ab","tid":1776404,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee5931baaeaf9e827b9f311aa1904951ee00497b","tid":1776404,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"387944f62d4a6c9b0c8f8c5f4123f250aca10bc7","tid":1776404,"uid":68943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:42:26.000Z","msg":"真開心 最憎人ig扮到有幾黃咪又係吃喝玩樂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:48:32.000Z","msg":"今日先知道得我一個唔慶祝"},{"pid":"7390f052a3ebe5c895bcab4585df5c8f7df948a3","tid":1776404,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kucMp8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkucMp8c.png&h=33c96d8f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}